## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of the topic. The reliance on secondary sources such as flashcards and articles may limit the depth of analysis. Additionally, cultural influences are complex and multifaceted, and this report may not capture all nuances. Further research, including primary data collection, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.